questions.text: What subjects do you enjoy most in school?
What activities make you lose track of time?
questions.answer: Coding personal projects and solving algorithm problems

questions.text: Do you prefer working with people, data, or things?
questions.answer: I love working with data and building things, but also enjoy collaborating with others

questions.text: What type of work environment appeals to you?
questions.answer: Hybrid work with some remote flexibility

questions.text: How important is work-life balance to you?
questions.answer: Very important - I want to have time for hobbies and personal projects
